title: Music Therapy
description: WC Partners has partnered with the Center for Music Therapy and Wellness to bring music therapy classes to Marshfield. Once a week, practitioners from the Center for Music Therapy and Wellness come and engage with individuals we serve to promote communication and interaction through music therapy.
